Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we return to the beta world line...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we undo that first D-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:09.02,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Being Meltdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep lying there, you'll get heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sleep on the roof of the lab \Nall the time, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's cloudy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida said he couldn't find her at Comima...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met up with her after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WTF?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you warn me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm soaked, down to my underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, Christina, for not listen—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's your fault for wearing such thin clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten you were such a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd want to see your stick figure in the nude...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more word, and I turn \Nyour neocortex into a flower pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of threat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got scratched somewhere, \Nwhen I was looking for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm classified as a "mad scientist"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a sewing kit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sewing kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I consider myself more family-oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's dark, so don't expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can look forward to finding out, \Nafter we leave, what color thread I used.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black, red, pink...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a 33% chance of each one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just pray it isn't pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in that stick figure of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you... A flower pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you have to go, \Nto rip your clothes like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I went to the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the laundry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then to your hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel? You stopped by?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't answer my messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't picking up your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As head of the lab, \Nit's my job to keep track of my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in the stick figure \Nof a nude mad scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place I was stabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain and despair were too real for a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu. You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have hazy memories inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak, almost nonexistent memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just of being stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you, too... hazily...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How desperate you were to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you kept pressing forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even hurt and all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't made it back to your original world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you've kept going,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kept calling her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kept crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kept trying to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I see that face,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think about how important she is to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And about whether it's possible for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to truly care for another person that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the beta world line, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that better than anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to abandon you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there another way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about the following since yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Isn't there some other way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Isn't there something else we can do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I can't come up with anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except going to the beta world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to accept this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't abandon Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let her die and then keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What would the point of that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can run away, but that'll just make it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you time leap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't get past the 1% barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know until we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just see Mayuri die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you think I've watched her die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And again and again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't destroy me... \NThe number of times I see it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri's going to suffer and die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say it doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't affect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then your heart's already broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it really will break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times Mayuri died, \NI stopped being surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd gone numb without even knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I even waited before time leaping, \Njust to see when she'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it just stopped affecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere inside, I was calmly telling myself \Nthat I could do it over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, it will destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let her die, you'll regret it... I'm certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have come this far, \Nfrom the single wish to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stop, we'll always regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the first world line, before the D-mail was sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's best for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's what's best for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many times have we fought, \Nover these past twenty days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've made fun of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've talked about our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When my back was against the wall, \NI turned to Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurisu was the one who listened to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who believed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At eighteen, a genius with a \Npublished academic paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always calm, always strong-willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always so proud and nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But always so kind and honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her theories continually amazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I remembered everything she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watched everything she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wasn't just another lab member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To me, Makise Kurisu was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For suffering so much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what does it mean to change world lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the second you go to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll just disappear from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you trade places with another Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm dead in the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no guarantee that I'm going to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There could be another me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,amidst all the other, infinite world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our minds are connected and comprise "me."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that'd be wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be everywhere, in every time, at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great love for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a great belief in something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a great desire to pass on something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all those things surpass time itself and create "you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't that be wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't think of it as abandoning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the world line changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you don't forget me, I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget the person I care for most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How... It's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face... Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't want to do that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But experiences, such as your first kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are stored in the hippocampus with your \Nstrong memories are harder to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bratty virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first kiss wasn't at all romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That last one only left a weak impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forget, not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll take extra care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a kiss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time is passing so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, I feel like complaining to Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether time is slow or fast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}depends on perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Relativity theory is so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure about not saying it to Mayuri and Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seeing me off would just make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can leave Japan without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I upgraded it to version 2.67.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll take it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you throwing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure, whatever happens, you're going to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only you will remember me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in a world where no one else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More than anyone else, you care for your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so that'll be painful for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But somehow, I'm glad you'll have that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those times when you're sitting around the lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you drink a can of juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you walk around town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And someday, when you kiss someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't have to be every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can be one time out of a hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'd like you to remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I'll be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be there, beyond the 1% barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we delete this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now begin the final phase of Operation Verdandi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our victory is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have overcome all conspiracies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upholding our ideals to the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, we have fought through \Nthe battle of Ragnarok!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank those who have worked so hard for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to ensure this victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful to all those I have had to sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What comes now is the world I wished for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all the choice of Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be rebuilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:19:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Lab Member 004?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,004?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't an 004.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the battle of Ragnarok has ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma, \Nhave controlled time itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,foiling the Organization and SERN's schemes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bringing about complete victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's ruling structure has been reset!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a future of chaos awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the choice of Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just issued a declaration of victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to talk like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can cry for yourself, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We no longer need the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of it, I met Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But because of it, so many were hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as Hououin Kyouma has died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Phone Microwave should die, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Living should mean no do-overs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is for the best. Right, Kurisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:01.27,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:04.02,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, there's a mysterious girl \Nwho wants to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the Radio Building's roof immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hashida Itaru's daughter, Amane Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe what I'm about to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must stop World War III.
